00:37:18,420 --> 00:37:22,720
♫  I think a sparkling love has finally come to me  ♫

578
00:37:22,720 --> 00:37:24,870
Hold on a moment.

579
00:37:26,190 --> 00:37:32,750
♫  You can tell me now that you feel the same way  ♫

